{"tid":1233201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Po 一張圖，唔係搞分化，只係想帶出一個信息","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:52:11.000Z","uid":132025,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de3d488e599902a959b6db6767d1d8fe5011c284","tid":1233201,"uid":132025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:48:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>切勿神化梁烈唯</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/weibo-01_1g1ZV_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fweibo-01_1g1ZV_1200x0.png&h=64158ed6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好唔記得人哋喺政協，15年雨革喺企我哋對面個班人，喺支持警察。而家佢企出嚟，可能喺身有屎，亦都可能真係有心為左香港。但係佢唔值得被我哋捧上神檯。我唔會讚佢或者屌佢牆頭草，只係想講唔好神化佢，保持危機感。<br />\n純屬小弟劣件，隨便負皮屌我"},{"pid":"b9df93ec5c01c38ca91c659e8db8ed3d33799a6f","tid":1233201,"uid":132025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:53:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"956cab990ebbbfa0615f27b61f3d32996ddc66cb","tid":1233201,"uid":99640,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:35:18.000Z","msg":"分唔到我真心咗定你真心咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef0f3f511ab678d0d9734987c36ccc79b949b74","tid":1233201,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"956cab990ebbbfa0615f27b61f3d32996ddc66cb","tid":1233201,"uid":99640,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:35:18.000Z","msg":"分唔到我真心咗定你真心咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:52:00.000Z","msg":"就結果然言，都唔認該放呢啲人上神檯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84f1dc97939d8fad7858437b787ee6bb479bb8","tid":1233201,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ef0f3f511ab678d0d97349